metadata.name: Pluto Enters Aquarius 1/1000
metadata.description:
Pluto enters Aquarius: March 23, 2023
Pluto retrograde enters Capricorn: June 11, 2023
Pluto enters Aquarius: January 21, 2024
Pluto retrograde enters Capricorn: September 2, 2024
Pluto enters Aquarius: November 19, 2024
Pluto enters Pisces: January 19, 2044

Pluto only dips a toe into Aquarius for now, it will not fully settle in Aquarius until January 20th 2024 where it will remain for 20 years.

Pluto will leave Aquarius January 2044.
 
Aquarius is ruled by Uranus, and its element, air. Uranus represents change, rebellion, and innovation, which often translates to breaking societal norms and challenging the status quo. This progressive mindset naturally aligns with the pursuit of social justice, as it involves advocating for equality, fairness, and true justice for the collective human family.

Pluto obliterates what is no longer useful. During this period we can be certain that longstanding systems of abuse and injustice will crumble to dust never to rise again.
